data.description: 100% FINANCING AVAILABLE. Seller to pay $6500 towards buyers closing cost and/or buying down interest rates with acceptable offer, Great home in Oak Lake Subdivision. Inviting open Floor Plan, Granite countertops, Stainless appliances, Gas Range. Formal dining room/office, Spacious LOFT area upstairs. Primary Suite features double vanity sinks and oversized soaker tub. Master bedroom located on first floor. Close access to I-10 for BR & New Orleans. Tons of amenities to enjoy including Lakes, fountains & walking trails. Priced to move. X Flood zone. Two car garage and large backyard. LISTED FOR SALE and for LEASE MLS 2425705
